            . I am the wife of Edward Singleton; we work for Mr. Lloyd in the Commercial-road. I sent my little boy out with these trousers, and he came back and said the person in my house had got them.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. PHILLIPS. Q. Have you not known her some time? Q. Yes, these twenty years; her husband has deserted her, and she has been rather distressed in her mind - I never knew her guilty of any bad act before.</p>
               <p>
            
